<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/910117-can-anyone-comment-on-the-content-of-this">Can anyone comment on the content of this book from a &#39;Parental Guidance&#39; standpoint? I&#39;m specifically concerned with profanity (especially blasphemy), and sexual content. I&#39;d like to listen to this on a road trip but will have kids in the vehicle.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_910117'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F101599.The_Guns_of_the_South">like</a></span>

