<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/48000748-mario"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/48000748-mario">Mario</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">There is some level of profanity and references to sexual content (especially prostitution). The most concerning thing for parents is probably the ext<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">There is some level of profanity and references to sexual content (especially prostitution). The most concerning thing for parents is probably the extremely common usage of the 'n-word'.<br /><br />Otherwise, most of book's content is appropriate to all ages.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
